data.text:
Post by coopmusic416 on

Just thought I'd let you guys know that the New Orleans Brass Funk Band Bonerama is heading out on tour for the summer and have announced their upcoming July dates, and it looks like a really full month!

July 1 - Fitzgerald's 30th American Music Festival - Berwyn, IL

July 2/3 - CityFolk Festival - Dayton, OH

July 4 - The Livery - Benton Harbor, MI

July 15 - Jazz In The Park - Milwaukee, WI

July 16 - Martyrs' - Chicago, IL

July 23 - WorkPlay Theatre - Birmingham, AL

July 24 - Rock N Bowl - New Orleans, LA

July 29 - Smith's Olde Bar - Atlanta, GA

July 30 - The Pour House - Charleston, SC

July 31 - Eastern Music Festival - Greensboro, NC

If you guys have never really heard Bonerama, I'd highly suggest checking out their Bandcamp Site.
